summary: Experienced manager and business director with a demonstrated history in international project management, business advisory services and training and finance for the international trade and development  sector. Extensive international consulting experience (.30 years) in Sustainable Development, Public-Private Partnerships,  Business Development, Value Chain Analysis, and Corporate Sustainability. Experience in more than 40 different countries in Africa, Asia, Middle East, Latin America and Europe.
